slidelink.displaytext: Select your language or Bhasha ka chunav krein
Q.1 (Hindi) Aramex export pickup karne ke liye jayein to kin kin cheezo ko sath lekar jayein? (English) What are the things you must carry before going for Aramex export pickup?
Q.2 (Hindi) Kis prakar ke shipments mei Multi-piece shipments (MPS) ho sakte hain? (English) In which scenario of export shipments can have MPS?
Q.3 (Hindi) Aapko client/seller location par hi har shipments ko FM app se manifest karna hoga. (English) You have to manifest every shipment on FM app at the location of client/seller.
Q.4 (Hindi) Shipments seller se lete waqt humein kon konse documents ki jarurat padti hai? (English) What are the important documents, we should check before picking any shipment from seller?
Q.5 (Hindi) Aapko seller ya client se COP cash on pickup cases me freight duty amount nahi lena hai. (English) You dont have to collect any amount from the seller/client in case of freight duty.
Q.6 (Hindi) Agar shipment document type hai to humein use kahan rakhna chahiye? (English) If shipment is document type where shall we put the shipment?
Q.7 (Hindi) Agar shipment ke sath invoice hai to wo commercial shipment nahi hai. (English) If invoice is available with shipment, it can not be a commercial shipment.

Q.8 (Hindi) Agar shipment ke sath invoice available hai to aapko shipment par bhi commercial ka sticker paste karna hoga. (English) If invoice is available with shipment, you also have to paste commercial sticker on shipment.
Q.9 (Hindi) Cash Recon System (CRS) kis platform ke dwara access kiya jata hai? (English) By which platform can we access Cash Recon System (CRS)?
Q.10 (Hindi) Cash on pickup (COP) ke case me shipment ko Picked kab mark kiya jata hai? (English) When does shipment status need to be marked as Picked in case of COP (Cash on Pickup)?
Q.11 (Hindi) LR Copy kya hai? (English) What is LR Copy?

Q.12 (Hindi) Agar shipment ki value 25,000 se jyada hai to aapko kin documents ko seller/client se lena hai? (English) If the shipment value is above 25,000, Which documents do we need to take from the seller/client?

Q.13 (Hindi) MPS shipments aur without waybill ke case me, hume generated waybill number ko manually kahan likhna padta hai? (English) In case of MPS shipments and without waybill , Where do we need to write generated waybill number?

Q.14 (Hindi) CRS (Cash Recon System) me Exception jaise ki Cash Lost, Package Lost add karne ke liye kis option ka use karte hai? (English) To add exception such as Cash Lost, Package Lost, Which option do we use in CRS (Cash Recon System)?
